{"word":"H5786 - עָוַר - ʻâvar - aw-var' - Blind","slug":"H5786","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָוַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻâvar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>aw-var'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Blind"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E2;&#x05D5;&#x05E8; - &#x201B;a&#x0302;var</b> - <i>aw-var'</i><p/>A primitive root (rather denominative from <a href=\"#/H5785\">H5785</a> through the idea of a <i>film</i> over the eyes); to <i>blind</i>: - blind, put out. See also <a href=\"#/H5895\">H5895</a>."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5787\">H5787</a>, <a href=\"#/H5788\">H5788</a>"}]}